narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: Purpose of graphic design and how to better communicate ideas to an audience
I learned a lot about the concepts in graphic design and gained a lot of experience in designing my own projects.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: None. It was well structured and had clear instructions. Extremely enjoyable class

Strengths: I gained a lot of feedback on my projects in every class.

I don't think there is any weakness.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes. The class is effective in allowing the student to gain insight on the fundamentals of graphic design and aesthetics.
For students who want to learn how to express ideas through images, color, and other elements of visual art, this is the course for them to choose.

narratives.question_text: The Canvas course site allowed me to identify and access required course materials easily.
How will you use the knowledge and skills you learned in this course in your future endeavors?
comments: I intend to use the material I have learnt in this class to better my artistic eye in terms of UIUX design and other graphic design needs.
The knowledge and skills I learned about graphic design enabled me to better understand how to convey ideas through visual images, which will help me study films in the future.
